OL,3,CDementia patients shape design of new
OL,4,Cmental health unit in Kent
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Kit Bradshaw was
OL,7,Fshown around Ruby Ward ahead of
OL,8,Fopening day
OL,10,FA new mental health unit, designed
OL,11,Fspecifically for older patients, has
OL,12,Fopened in Kent.
OL,14,FThe 16-bed Ruby Ward is housed in a
OL,15,Fnew stand-alone building, close to
OL,16,FMaidstone Hospital.
OL,18,FThe facility will treat those with
OL,19,Fsevere and complex mental health needs
OL,20,Fbut many patients are also likely to
OL,21,Fbe living with dementia.
