OL,3,CDementia patients shape design of new
OL,4,Cmental health unit in Kent
OL,6,FThe new #12.6 million unit replaces
OL,7,Fthe outdated inpatient services
OL,8,Fpreviously located at Medway Maritime
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FThe building has dementia-friendly
OL,12,Fsignage and colour-coded doors.
OL,14,FSheila Stenson, chief executive of
OL,15,FKent and Medway NHS and Social Care
OL,16,FPartnership, said: "Not only will Ruby
OL,17,Fcreate a better day every day for our
OL,18,Fpatients, it will also increase our
OL,19,Fcapacity to support older people with
OL,20,Fmental health needs.
