OL,6,F"The new unit offers a modern working
OL,7,Fenvironment for our hard-working staff
OL,8,Fand is designed specifically to meet
OL,9,Fthe needs of older adults with complex
OL,10,Fmental health illness, such as
OL,11,Fdementia, providing an environment
OL,12,Fthat will help manage our patients'
OL,13,Fsymptoms better and support their care
OL,14,Fneeds."
