OL,3,CDementia patients shape design of new
OL,4,Cmental health unit in Kent
OL,6,FHelen Whately, MP for Faversham and
OL,7,FMid Kent, said: "We've invested an
OL,8,Fextra #2.3 billion in mental health
OL,9,Fservices since 2019, and replacing
OL,10,Foutdated dormitories is just part of
OL,11,Fthat. Extra funding for research,
OL,12,Ftalking therapies, and crisis support
OL,13,Fare all making a difference for people
OL,14,Facross Kent and Medway."
OL,16,FThe investment is part of an NHS
OL,17,FEngland drive to eradicate 'dormitory'
OL,18,Fstyle wards in inpatient mental health
OL,19,Ffacilities.
